reams-al-ruyaa","tag-hellfire-nar-jahannam","tag-hereafter-akhirah","tag-manners-adab","tag-negligence-al-ghaflah","tag-obligations-faraid","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-punishment-al-uqubah","tag-al-quran","tag-sleep-al-nawm","tag-laziness-sloth-al-kasl","tag-warning-al-nudhr"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-akC","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":3852,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/27\/surah-ikhlaas-third-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":39718,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Surat al-Ikhlas worth one-third of Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa'id al-Khudri reported: A man heard another man reciting, \"Say, He is Allah, the One,\" (112:1) again and again. The next morning he came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and told him about it, as if he thought it was not enough to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11977,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/01\/recite-quran-month-seven-days\/","url_meta":{"origin":39718,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Read entire Quran once every month","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 1, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRead the Quran once in every month.\u201d I said, \u201cI have strength to do more.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThen read it in twenty nights.\u201d I said, \u201cI have strength to do more.\u201d The Prophet said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3849,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/27\/surat-al-ikhlas-third-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":39718,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Read a third of the Book in a night?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said to his companions, \u201cIs it difficult for one of you to recite a third of the Quran in a single night?\u201d That was difficult for them, so they said, \u201cWhich one of us can do that, O\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25027,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/28\/surah-al-fatihah-enough\/","url_meta":{"origin":39718,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Recitation: Surat al-Fatihah is enough, more is better","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 28, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ata\u2019 reported: Abu Huraira, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIn every prayer is a recitation. Prayers that were recited aloud by the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, we have recited aloud to you, and what he recited silently, we have kept silent with you. Whoever recites\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3896,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/29\/subhan-ruku-dua-sujud\/","url_meta":{"origin":39718,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Glorify Allah in bowing, supplicate in prostration","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO people, there are no more glad tidings of prophecy except righteous dreams seen by a Muslim, or he is made to see. Verily, I have been prohibited from reciting the Quran while bowing or prostrating\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2744,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/02\/taalam-al-quran-wa-allamahu\/","url_meta":{"origin":39718,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Best Muslims learn the Quran and teach it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Uthman bin Affan reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"The best of you are those who learn the Quran and teach it.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5027 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u062b\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\